---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-100 py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-5xl">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-800">About IdiomasPuentes</h1>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center mb-16 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <img src="/images/tribal-church.jpg" alt="Tribal Church" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-1/2 p-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-700">Our Purpose</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          IdiomasPuentes is a convergence of churches united by God's call to support tribal churches. We equip them to translate the Word of God and bring discipleship and Bible study resources into the language of their heart.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          We strive to see the profound joy and spiritual transformation that occurs when a community hears the Bible spoken in their mother tongue.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="mb-16 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-6 text-gray-700">Bridge Languages</h2>
      <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
        <Icon name="mdi:earth" class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-500 mr-4" />
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
          Bridge languages, primarily Spanish and Portuguese, serve as crucial links between communities with different native tongues. They play a vital role in our mission by:
        </p>
      </div>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg text-gray-600 ml-4 space-y-2">
        <li>Facilitating the initial translation of resources from major world languages</li>
        <li>Serving as a stepping stone for further translation into local languages</li>
        <li>Enabling communication and collaboration across different linguistic communities</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-6 text-gray-700">Church-Centric Bible Translation</h2>
      <p class="text-lg mb-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        We believe in empowering the tribal Church to undertake the task of translating the Word of God. This approach, known as Church-Centric Bible Translation (CCBT), recognizes that:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg text-gray-600 ml-4 space-y-2 mb-6">
        <li>God has given the tribal Church the desire and calling to complete Bible translations</li>
        <li>The Global Church is called to serve the tribal Church by providing necessary tools and training</li>
        <li>This process contributes to the growth and strengthening of the Church</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/ccbt" class="inline-block bg-blue-500 text-white py-2 px-6 rounded-full hover:bg-blue-600 transition duration-300 ease-in-out font-semibold">Learn more about CCBT &rarr;</a>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>
